desc:
Between two extremes \
A feeling of not being belonged \
High expectations \
A feeling of being forced \
 \
And yet not quite there \
And yet not able to satisfy myself. \
To feel comfortable \
To feel safe \
 \
A journey through feelings and thoughts \
A journey through myself \
Through my understanding of pleasure \
Through the binaries\
\
Eine Performance von: Kira Porbasas
title: Not Quite There Yet
